commits.author: Yonik Seeley
commits.sourceNew: /** * Retrieves the date of the last modification for the given id * * @param entryId - * the entry Id * @param feedId - * the feed which contains the entry * @return - The date of the last modifiaction in milliseconds or * new Long(0) if the resource can not be found eg. * the time can not be accessed * @throws StorageException - * if the storage can not be accessed */ public Long getEntryLastModified(String entryId, String feedId) throws StorageException;
